{
    "info": {
        "name": "Incredible API - Getting Started (Updated)",
        "description": "Complete collection for testing Incredible API chat completion endpoint.\n\nIMPORTANT: Response Format\n=========================\nThe API returns responses in this nested format:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"result\": {\n    \"response\": [\n      {\n        \"content\": \"AI response text here...\",\n        \"role\": \"assistant\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"thinking\": \"AI reasoning process...\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nTo extract the actual response text, use: `result.result.response[0].content`",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "base_url",
            "value": "https://api.incredible.one",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "api_key",
            "value": "your_api_key_here",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "user_id",
            "value": "your_user_id_here",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "1. Basic Chat Completion",
            "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                    {
                        "key": "Content-Type",
                        "value": "application/json"
                    },
                    {
                        "key": "Authorization",
                        "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}"
                    }
                ],
                "body": {
                    "mode": "raw",
                    "raw": "{\n    \"model\": \"small-1\",\n    \"stream\": false,\n    \"system\": \"You are a helpful AI assistant.\",\n    \"messages\": [\n        {\n            \"role\": \"user\",\n            \"content\": \"Hello! Can you explain what APIs are in simple terms?\"\n        }\n    ]\n}"
                },
                "url": {
                    "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/chat-completion",
                    "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                    "path": ["v1", "chat-completion"]
                }
            },
            "response": [
                {
                    "name": "Success Example",
                    "originalRequest": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"model\": \"small-1\",\n    \"stream\": false,\n    \"messages\": [\n        {\n            \"role\": \"user\",\n            \"content\": \"What is 2+2?\"\n        }\n    ]\n}"
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/v1/chat-completion",
                            "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                            "path": ["v1", "chat-completion"]
                        }
                    },
                    "status": "OK",
                    "code": 200,
                    "body": "{\n  \"result\": {\n    \"response\": [\n      {\n        \"content\": \"2 + 2 = 4\",\n        \"role\": \"assistant\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"thinking\": \"This is a simple arithmetic question. 2 + 2 equals 4.\"\n  }\n}"
                }
            ]
        },
